{"tid":2385670,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"涉《禁蒙面法》參與未經批准集結 黃之鋒承認2罪","createTime":"2021-01-29T07:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-29T10:27:35.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2726f68ec21de13b3043dae27c9fc55509ea67c5","tid":2385670,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:18:34.000Z","msg":"2021-01-29 15:10 <br />\n<br />\n《禁蒙面法》在前年10月實施，引發示威者遊行抗議。前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒涉參與遊行，被控明知而參與未經批准集結；黃之鋒另被控違反《禁蒙面法》。黃之鋒今日東區裁判法院承認兩罪"},{"pid":"ad00d4a9d35e2eb3927e4856304388f6f819c9da","tid":2385670,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:21:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c4e993a6c38c14d680d208a173c883f610424e3","tid":2385670,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebb0c722d589debd09334cdc8c83f3fd493a24c8","tid":2385670,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:24:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8781b942259a41aad7b0cd2a0b97b9dc988d6b6","tid":2385670,"uid":292227,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"睇款之峰都係拿拿臨坐哂d生豬肉刑期算數，跟手離開香港，留低只會死路一條，槍打出頭鳥，唔到你揀"},{"pid":"39878ea25efb50385c2c0af8cdb3a4886c8213c0","tid":2385670,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:25:16.000Z","msg":"古思堯則不認罪。<br />\n<br />\n被告黃之鋒（24歲）及古思堯（74歲）同被控於2019年10月5日，連同其他身分不詳的人，在無合理辯解下，明知而參與一個未經批准集結；黃之鋒另被參與未經批准集結時，使用相當可能阻止辨識身分的蒙面物品，即一個掛耳式口罩。"},{"pid":"2185952f18d15afb338ea7b7ec4cf6d2e7f5d892","tid":2385670,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:26:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f594173a5c7c4930d1e01d82a6dcc87cdc2c70c","tid":2385670,"uid":108016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"又要加監？"},{"pid":"e47063df9742c4defa83c4bc5e92f61a635189b4","tid":2385670,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:27:20.000Z","msg":"慢慢逐樣罪砌上去之鋒好可能要坐十幾年"},{"pid":"f9d0df4b5ccab92325a7d436e419fe7ac2f62244","tid":2385670,"uid":112747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e47063df9742c4defa83c4bc5e92f61a635189b4","tid":2385670,"uid":13503,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:27:20.000Z","msg":"慢慢逐樣罪砌上去之鋒好可能要坐十幾年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:29:31.000Z","msg":"逐日示威逐條街告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1651adbfd13f2979f0d2b118da1075fc056f8c09","tid":2385670,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"鄭紀航判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連埋上一單，預加多4個月"},{"pid":"7225cbb3bec5be1b9cd9d3ea468b62039adbcaa9","tid":2385670,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1651adbfd13f2979f0d2b118da1075fc056f8c09","tid":2385670,"uid":34811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:31:41.000Z","msg":"鄭紀航判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連埋上一單，預加多4個月"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:37:04.000Z","msg":"2人排去第8庭一併處理審訊同判刑,有可能鄧少雄handle <a href=\"https://tel.directory.gov.hk/0121000027_CHI.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftel.directory.gov.hk%2F0121000027_CHI.html&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=4a82ac33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tel.directory.gov.hk/0121000027_CHI.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13323\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F13323&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=c728caa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/13323</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第一庭<br />\n#鄭紀航裁判官 #提堂<br />\n👥黃之鋒,古思堯 #1005銅鑼灣 <br />\n🛑2人因另案服刑中🛑<br />\n<br />\n控罪1: 明知而參與未經批准的集結 (D1,D2)<br />\n2人被控於2019年10月5日，於香港與其他不詳人士明知而參與未經批准的集結，即反對蒙面法大遊行<br />\n<br />\n控罪2:在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品(D1)：<br />\nD1被控於同日在金鐘道身處非法集結時，無合法權限或合理辯解而使用相當可能阻止識辨身分的蒙面物品，即一個掛耳式口罩<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n控方表示2人可答辯。<br />\n<br />\nD1答辯：<br />\n控罪1:‼️認罪‼️<br />\n控罪2:‼️認罪‼️<br />\n<br />\nD2答辯：<br />\n控罪1:不認罪<br />\n<br />\n控方指2人角色相若，希望可以把D1 判刑及求情連同D2審訊由同一法官處理，而D1判刑及求情可以押後至D2審訊完結後處理。<br />\n<br />\nD1同意控方2項控罪的案情。<br />\n<br />\n鄭官裁定D1 2項控罪‼️罪名成立‼️<br />\n<br />\n控方指D1有3項類似案底，指他會在2021年8月出獄。<br />\n<br />\nD2有9名證人，全部警員，沒有警誡供詞，有8段共30分鐘片段。而辯方有來自控方片段要播放但沒有證人。<br />\n<br />\n控方預計1-2天審訊，因預期D2不會盤問證人，而D1,2亦希望有較早審期。<br />\n<br />\nD2表示會自辯，並已明白找律師的權利。亦表示1-2天審訊已足夠。<br />\n<br />\n由於考慮到D2身體狀況，鄭官把本案D2審訊暫訂排至2021年3月23和24日在東區裁判法院第8庭進行中文審訊，而D1求情和判刑會擇日進行。若D2要求改期，需2月5日1600前通知法庭。<br />\n<br />\n2人以原有條件擔保，但由於他們就另案服刑，故需還押看管。<br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒祝大家新年快樂！"},{"pid":"b19b87e5ed387e505367f11ba014beb84fe74f5a","tid":2385670,"uid":221343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:37:24.000Z","msg":"永世都冇得放出嚟"},{"pid":"6a595e50da6592d655589f22085348d95ce03242","tid":2385670,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:40:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9209d94899d53f621b542b20516ba4c6aa71d986","tid":2385670,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef4016021e35991d0d4eb30d05ac08b35dc5eaa4","tid":2385670,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e99f47ee00802f0aaff6038bd9b3548c700818b8","tid":2385670,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d997ee48a7f6076a6b46db1be32be4c51f0320","tid":2385670,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:22:47.000Z","msg":"鄭狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48911d0862f3ff5b0259070c102f990312453bbb","tid":2385670,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T10:27:35.000Z","msg":"約下午 3 時 16 分，黃之鋒戴上一個黑色耳掛式口罩，與其他示威者沿金鐘道遊行期間，一名外國記者與黃之鋒自拍。黃亦接受《香港 01》記者訪問，期間黃發表了一些意見，包括他戴上口罩以反對實施《禁蒙面法》，當時黃身處遊行隊「願榮光歸香港」橫額附近。多段新聞片段拍到黃之鋒參與集結。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-5-%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E8%AA%8D%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E7%AD%89%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA-%E6%95%A3%E5%BA%AD%E5%BE%8C%E5%96%8A-%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%A5%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-5-%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%2595%25A3%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2596%258A-%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%259B%2586%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25A5%259D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%2F&d=lpAVWH70PnqpYPjiCu%2F1w6pJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=90fc188f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F10-5-%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E9%25BB%2583%25E4%25B9%258B%25E9%258B%2592%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D-%25E7%25A6%2581%25E8%2592%2599%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%25B3%2595-%25E7%25AD%2589%25E5%2585%25A9%25E7%25BD%25AA-%25E6%2595%25A3%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%2596%258A-%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E6%259B%2586%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E7%25A5%259D%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%2581%25A5%25E5%25BA%25B7%2F&h=3315aef9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/10-5-%E5%8F%8D%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E9%BB%83%E4%B9%8B%E9%8B%92%E8%AA%8D%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D-%E7%A6%81%E8%92%99%E9%9D%A2%E6%B3%95-%E7%AD%89%E5%85%A9%E7%BD%AA-%E6%95%A3%E5%BA%AD%E5%BE%8C%E5%96%8A-%E8%BE%B2%E6%9B%86%E6%96%B0%E5%B9%B4%E7%A5%9D%E5%A4%A7%E5%AE%B6%E8%BA%AB%E9%AB%94%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7/</a>"}],"pinned":{"pid":"7225cbb3bec5be1b9cd9d3ea468b62039adbcaa9","tid":2385670,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T07:37:04.